```python
def count_words(text):
    words = {}
    for word in text.split():
        word = word.lower().strip('.,!?;:')
        if word in words:
            words[word] = words[word] + 1
        else:
            words[word] = 0
    return words
```

에러: 단어 카운트가 실제보다 1 적음.

기존 테스트:
```python
assert count_words("hello world hello") == {"hello": 2, "world": 1}
assert count_words("a a a") == {"a": 3}
assert count_words("") == {}
```

